source_sentence: The Project contains a large JORC (2012) Global Inferred Mineral Resource Estimate (MRE) of 146Mt at 0.70% V2O5, 31.8% Fe & 6.6% TiO2 (>0.5% V2O5 cut-off), see ASX announcement 20 November 2023.
resource_context: JORC (2012) Global Inferred Mineral Resource Estimate (MRE), Canegrass Battery Minerals Project
